title: Five Minutes to Zero (1960 Spy Thriler) Directed by Barry Mahon

sources.title: Five Minutes to Zero (1960 Spy Thriler) Directed by Barry Mahon
sources.description:
Moscow's Missile vs. Manhattan: Fears about Sputnik's capabilities prompt the U.S. to send agent John Manston undercover into Soviet territory. Teaming with operative Tanya, they discover the satellite has mapped New York City for a devastating strike. Their mission to sabotage the missile program collapses, leaving Manhattan's fate dependent on a faltering defense network.

Original Title: Rocket Attack U.S.A. (1960) | AKA: Five Minutes to Zero
